COMMANDS RUN to init sandbox: 
npm init
npm install --save-dev react webpack react-router react-hot-loader webpack-dev-server babel-loader redux

source:
http://jmfurlott.com/tutorial-setting-up-a-single-page-react-web-app-with-react-router-and-webpack/

webpack dev server basic setup:
https://webpack.github.io/docs/webpack-dev-server.html